main_body:
Every application for import rights lodged in accordance with Regulation (EC) No 1146/2003 for the period 1 July 2003 to 30 June 2004 shall be granted to the following extent, expressed as bone-in beef:
(a) 38,9831 % of the quantity requested for beef imports intended for the manufacture of "preserves" as defined by Article 3(1)(a) of Regulation (EC) No 1146/2003;
(b) 86,5494 % of the quantity requested for beef imports intended for the manufacture of products as defined by Article 3(1)(b) of Regulation (EC) No 1146/2003.
